latestIgtvVideos.title: Colour Lounge X American Crew
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Yesterday at Colour Lounge I had a chance to experience their new services with @americancrew and it's needless to say it was superb. 
It all started with deep cleansing to make sure that I had a clear base to work on the magic which was then followed by trimming and styling of my beard. Thereafter, scaling was done to enhance skin texture and get rid of dead skin cells which then culminated into the exhilarating experience of Vibrating Mask; massaging on the main points of the skin to improve blood circulation. 
What's more, my hair was styled to give it a rugged look and I was off to having a good night out! 
Visit the nearest branch today to get pampered at just ₹999/-
@suman_suruchi_chandni_mua @colourlounge_hair_skin_nails 
____________________________ 
A big shout out to my brother @that_clicker for shooting and editing! 📸
